title: The B-52's - Love Shack - [4K Ultra HD].mp4
description:
The Official video.

This video is in 4K 3840*2160 Ultra HD.

To play it on your 4K TV to fully enjoy and get it's full enjoyment
you will have to either play it from your computer through HDMI
or if your 4K TV has a media player you can load it on an external storage drive 
and run it through the USB port. You will be able to load this on a
flash drive stick and run it through your USB port on your 4K tv.

Someone asked me on another upload via comment...if it was good?

If I post it...it is good.

I will not post anything that is not good.

Everything I post is from my own stash I 
watch myself on my 4K tv.

I just noticed there wasn't much in the way for the people
who own 4K tv's.

So I thought I would share a little from my own private collection.

Everything I upload is for the 4K tv.

So play them on your 4K tv and enjoy!

And I figure if they are not worth people seeding 
and keeping them alive for the leaches then they are not worth it for me 
to seed them and keep them alive for the leaches
